channel.name: wildlife-sanctuary-challenge
channel.topic:
Design and build a safe refuge for our Earth mob friends! Populate your sanctuary with as many or few mobs and mob variants as you want. Show off how you imagine our mob friends in their safe habitat!
Challenge dates: April 14 – April 27

messages.content:
Wildlife Sanctuary Build Challenge! 🌳:muddy_pig::cluckshroom::horned_sheep:🌳

With Earth Day coming up, let’s pause for a second and appreciate our planet. In the same spirit, design and populate your own wildlife sanctuary with all the lively mobs and their variants in their safe habitat. Feel free to use as many or as few mob variants as you want and show off how you imagine these mobs in their safe habitat!

:timer: Challenge dates: April 14 – April 27

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! Challenge theme is open to interpretation and buildplate size won’t be a factor in judging.
:sign: Post your image or video submission and buildplate share link in #wildlife-sanctuary-challenge by the deadline. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges: Winning submissions may be used in social media posts.
:fast_parrot: Have fun!
Give our mob friends a nice safe place to live! Looking adorable all the time is tough work for them! :muddy_pig_mini:
Don't forget to include those fancy new buildplate share links! :buildplate:🔗
